#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/author_settings.rst:20
msgid "The main element is the Author page. This page was overhauled massively in 4.0."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/author_settings.rst:22
msgid "By default, it will use the \"Anonymous\" profile, which contains nothing. To create a new profile, press the \"+\" button, and write up a name for the author profile."
